---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Content } from '@docs/encryption-architecture.md';
---

<Layout title="Rapid">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-4xl">Welcome to Rapid</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">Your marketing content goes here.</p>
  </div>

  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="rounded-xl border bg-card p-6 shadow-sm">
      <div class="encryption-diagram overflow-x-auto">
        <Content />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-lg border bg-card p-4">
        <h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-lg">Key Derivation</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
          PBKDF2-SHA256 with 600,000 iterations transforms your password into a
          cryptographically secure 256-bit key, following OWASP 2023
          recommendations.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border bg-card p-4">
        <h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-lg">Platform Security</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
          Each platform uses native encryption: SQLCipher on mobile,
          ChaCha20-Poly1305 on desktop, and SQLite3MultipleCiphers in the
          browser.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border bg-card p-4">
        <h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-lg">Memory Safety</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
          Encryption keys are securely zeroed from memory after use, preventing
          extraction from memory dumps or swap files.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .encryption-diagram :global(h1),
  .encryption-diagram :global(h2),
  .encryption-diagram :global(h3) {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .encryption-diagram :global(h1) {
    font-size: 1.875rem;
  }

  .encryption-diagram :global(h2) {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .encryption-diagram :global(h3) {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .encryption-diagram :global(p) {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-muted-foreground);
  }

  .encryption-diagram :global(svg) {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    min-width: 800px;
  }
</style>
